@disagreeable
What I did
navigate to iPad/Apps/com.jeppesen.JeppFD/Documents/data
delete the 4 folders (airway_manuals, Enroute, enroute_notices, TermCharts)
copy the 4 folders from this torrent.
Then just open jeppFD and select demo mode. Wait a few seconds/minutes to build the charts database, after that you should have all the IFR charts

Hi folks.
For those who are trying to unlock the JeppFD software (1.1.0 version) and are having troubles, here are the step by step procedures you need to do it:
1. Install JeppFD on device and open the software for the first time.
2. Download the 1205 cycle on the link: http://thepiratebay.se/torrent/7073191/Jeppview_1205
3. Unzip the file named 1205.zip
4. On the iExplorer, navigate to iPad name/Apps/JeppFD
5. Replace the folder " Documents " for the folder you unziped with the same name.

  After that, you just need to continue updating the cycles!!!
 I hope you have succes!!!
